                    <span>Wow! What a wonderful book! David Borher has to be one of the most talented photographers I've seen in a while. The insight he provided on America's Special Forces was not only informative, it was ENTERTAINING. This is a book that everyone should own. People don't know enough about the special forces here in the U.S. In this book, Mr. Borher goes inside the different realms of the special forces of America and does a hell of a job showing us what it's all about! I can only hope he will put together another book in the near future, I know I'll be the first one in line to buy it!</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Lucky13 is a fool</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
